Good evening Hustlepeople!Sunday reflection/reminder:‚ÄúLearn to take losses. The most important thing in making money is not letting your losses out of hand.‚Äù- Martin SchwartzBlessed Sunday to all. Friday was pretty bad for most I reckon. This could be an eye opener for the newer players and just a sneak on brutal market can get. I would say this coming week is going to be a very important week. Best to sidelines and watch for an indication of what might follow. Hence  best to stay out of new positions first and if there are profit to take/breakeven on existing trades  good to do so first. Ultimately  if market gets really bad  we are spared and losses minimised. BUT  We will come back stronger when the market indication is clearer.Safe Trading ALWAYS everyone.Let‚Äôs go!PS: Always remember to have a cut loss in place. This will be the big difference between a small loss and a big loss that can wipe you out.
